mpelling tale, encompassing three distinct regions of the British Atlantic, will be read by scholars across a range of fields.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 22. Okt 2019) 0aMaroonszJamaicaxHistory. 0aMaroonszNova ScotiaxHistory. 0aMaroonszSierra LeonexHistory. 7aHISTORY / Modern / 18th Century.2bisacsh40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300235227423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780300235227.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles